    Merely a rectangle which can check for overlap with another rectangle.

    A binary tree for detection.

    Face detection ImageJ plugin using 'imagingbook.violajones' implementation of the Viola-Jones face detection algorithm: Paul Viola and Michael Jones, "Robust Real-time Face Detection", International Journal of Computer Vision 57.2 (2004), pp.
    Gradient
    Used to calculate the gradient magnitude inside a given rectangular region.
    HaarCascadeDescriptor
    This class represents a trained Haar cascade classifier.

    This class gives easy access to the Haar training sets, obtained from OpenCV.

    Helper class for visualizing the detection process.
